        <p> Very small cages awaited us with bare concrete or tile floor, without any greenery, branches, water or other. But a lot of garbage in the cages and tourists who embarrassed the animals in the cages and took photos. Our companion could not understand that we did not want all of this and were looking for the width as quickly as possible. Our driver naturally wanted to make us happy with the butterflies and so we didn't say anything with him. However, we already decided that we have to work. </p>
        <p> Since this was the last stop on our day tour, we now went back towards the hotel. The journey lasted almost 1.5 hours and we actually ended up happily from the beautiful day, but very shocked by the last stop again in the resort. We thanked the driver, put a tip in his hand and first gone to the room. In the meantime I went on Facebook and searched for this supposed zoo and left a bad rating with various keywords so that it also opened up in all important organization. Basti then roughly translated them into English and also sent them directly to some organizations. Something needs to be done here and we hope that someone will work there. </p>
